			<div class="message-container"></div>
			<div class="buttons-container">
				<i class="fas fa-times close-btn"></i>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="footer">
			<div class="footer-label-and-move-to-top-container">
				<a href="/" class="label-container">
					<div class="label">zeerum</div>
				</a>
				<a href="#" class="move-to-top">Move to top</a>
			</div>

			<div class="footer-content">
				<div class="description">
					We are a community that shares ideas of beautiful minds. First started as a
